kpi.name: M1034C9

kpi_info.title: SUM SF256 CODE OCCUPANCY PER OPER
kpi_info.use: This counter, divided by the denominator counter M1034C10, indicates the average number of allocated Rel99 DL codes represented in SF256 level. For example one DCH using SF128 updates the counter by value 2 and one DCH using SF64 updates the counter by value 4. UPDATED: The code utilization is sampled with 1-second intervals.
